WEBVTT

00:02:30.548 --> 00:02:34.416
bizning yotog'imiz ostida, bizning 
bog'imizda

00:02:34.709 --> 00:02:37.867
yoki bizning kindigimizda mavjud 
mikroskopik hayotni

00:02:37.891 --> 00:02:39.310
fosh qilish ustida ishlayman.

00:02:40.083 --> 00:02:42.953
Men bu sohada ishlaganimni sababi 
biz bizga yaqin bo'lgan

00:02:42.977 --> 00:02:45.298
mikroskopik hayot haqida juda 
ham kam bilamiz.

00:02:46.281 --> 00:02:48.754
Bir necha yil muqaddam hech 
qaysi olim bizga yaxshi

00:02:48.778 --> 00:02:51.391
tanish bo'lgan xonadonimizda 
qanday parazit yoki

00:02:52.508 --> 00:02:55.931
mikroorganizm turishini aytolmasdi.

00:02:56.607 --> 00:02:58.347
Shuning uchun men va boshqa jamoalar

00:02:58.371 --> 00:03:00.564
paxta o'ralgan gurgurt cho'plari, 
pinsetlar va